  "1867740": {
    "name": "Like Dreamer",
    "steam_appid": 1867740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867740/extras/776b3d4ae28f8ed8ad54be16df53edd6.avif?t=1757559733\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款来自《Cosmo Dreamer》的作者【外の人（Outside）】的色彩缤纷、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱又充满幻想元素的弹幕射击游戏。游戏以弹幕系社交软件为主题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将在虚拟场景中躲避弹幕，凭借出色的游戏技巧赢得点赞和粉丝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然弹幕游戏常给人难度较高的印象，但请不必担心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作采用了对新手友好的设计，同时也能让高手体验到更具挑战性的游戏内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867740/extras/abc9e8b3ef15e7099eb1d948305baa76.avif?t=1757559733\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在当下流行的弹幕系社交软件“Bulletalk”中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少女们凭借精彩的弹幕游戏操作吸引眼球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得其他用户的点赞已然成为弹幕少女的圈子中的一种时尚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中点赞数和粉丝数最高的用户被大家称为弹幕女王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是有些用户嫉妒弹幕女王，肆意造谣中伤她。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被激怒的弹幕女王发起了反击，让那些中伤她的用户们成为弹幕战的目标！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场风波瞬间引爆网络！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自各大社群的敌人蜂拥而至！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场弹幕玩家之间的激烈战斗中，胜者的荣誉终将花落谁家？只有时间才能给出答案！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867740/extras/06f17f173801a02837d90aa3f5f6f400.avif?t=1757559733\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867740/extras/1135936919fe132288395598a827b2b0.avif?t=1757559733\" width=400 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢穿着性感COS服自拍投稿的成熟Cosplayer。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很喜欢可爱的东西和弹幕射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有着强烈的被人认可的渴望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867740/extras/2b4f826bd4256d3e695ccce653611900.avif?t=1757559733\" width=400 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自称黑猫系的高冷女高中生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对自己的外表非常自信，但缺点是嘴巴很毒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有着强烈的被人认可的渴望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867740/extras/32a8034122fd6cce2b01b96059c42785.avif?t=1757559733\" width=400 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >略微修改了Bulletalk的程序来游玩的天才型弹幕少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对弹幕女王抱有一些个人情绪，因而投身于激烈的弹幕对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一些被人认可的渴望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867740/extras/7b589540f364fd1c75e0d3641fb06261.avif?t=1757559733\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・自由选择战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・可从3位弹幕少女中选择一位，自定义射击方式与炸弹，打造独属于你的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・躲不好也没关系！&quot;活力计&quot;系统攻防一体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・通过持续射击积累活力计可提升活力等级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・活力等级提升后，即使中弹也会触发护盾抵消伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・还可以消耗活力等级发动强力的炸弹技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・引爆社交媒体！&quot;热度计&quot;系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・收获点赞与粉丝关注即可提升热度值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・热度计满时将在短时内开启&quot;高光时刻&quot;。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・期间玩家攻击力大幅提升！获得点赞数翻倍增长！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・从容进入下一关......关卡选择模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・每通过一个关卡将解锁新关卡，即使中途结束游戏也可从后续关卡继续游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・练习你不擅长的弹幕！「练习模式」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・在练习模式中，可自由设置从哪里开始以哪种状态开始游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・提供三种难度选择适应不同水平。证明自己的实力后还可以解锁更高的难度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・传统街机风格的「试炼模式」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・以及连续对战头目的「BOSS RUSH」等额外模式.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・达成特定条件即可解锁画廊中的插画与成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・你是否能集齐所有成就？</p>",
